<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>EventFlow Features</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="features.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>EventFlow Features</h1>
<p>Discover what makes our platform powerful for event management</p>
</header>

<section class="features">

<div class="card">
<h2>📅 Event Discovery</h2>
<p>Find upcoming events, seminars and workshops easily with smart search and filters.</p>
<button onclick="showFeature('event')">Learn More</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>📝 Easy Registration</h2>
<p>Register for events quickly with a simple RSVP and ticket booking system.</p>
<button onclick="showFeature('register')">Learn More</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>👤 Student Profile</h2>
<p>Manage your personal profile, view registered events and update information.</p>
<button onclick="showFeature('profile')">Learn More</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>🔔 Notifications</h2>
<p>Receive reminders and updates about events you registered for.</p>
<button onclick="showFeature('notify')">Learn More</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>📊 Dashboard</h2>
<p>Track your activities, upcoming events and event history in one place.</p>
<button onclick="showFeature('dashboard')">Learn More</button>
</div>

</section>

<div id="infoBox"></div>

<script src="features.js"></script>

</body>
</html>